<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

  <%= render 'layouts/head' %>

  <body>

    <%= render 'layouts/header' %>

    <!-- Main jumbotron for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
    <div class="jumbotron">
      <div class="container">
        <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/public-patron/LOGO-PNG3.png" class="img-responsive" alt="Responsive image"> 
        <h1>A MOVEMENT TO FREE CULTURE + <span class="jumbotext1">DISRUPT BIG MEDIA</span> BY SUPPORTING <span class="jumbotext2">CREATORS DIRECTLY</span></h1>
        <!-- <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="about" role="button">Learn more &raquo;</a></p> -->
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <!-- Example row of columns -->
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h2>For Creators</h2>
          <p>Artists want the freedom to express themselves. Journalists and educators want to honestly relay facts and ideas. With access to a worldwide audience over the internet, our platform allows each of them to be successful without having to compromise their independence.</p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/static_pages/the_big_idea" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h2>For Consumers</h2>
          <p>The internet connects us to all the world's media. But as businesses focus on profit and push content and limit access, they ruin the consumer experience. Let's embrace the open internet instead and give people what they want, when they want, on any device they choose. </p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/static_pages/the_big_idea" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
       </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h2>In the Public Interest</h2>
          <p>Moving society forward requires access to information and art. Our most important ideas challenge powerful interests and can therefore only exist if there is the freedom to develop them and the independence to share them. We exist to grow this kind of global cultural democracy.</p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/static_pages/the_big_idea" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr>

    </div> <!-- /container -->

  <%= render 'layouts/footer' %>

